      • permitEnter

        public boolean permitEnter(java.lang.String senderId,
                           long senderTimeStamp)
        when a request is received, decides if the process has access to critical section with the criteria set on the Ricart and Argawala's algorithm.
        Parameters:
        senderId - the process's id of the request's sender
        senderTimeStamp - the lamport counter value of the request's sender at the moment of the build of request
        Returns:
        true if the request is accepted and false if the request should be queued
